body_html: I have been working on a painful private project for a while using Swift. I'll be migrating the project API library to Swift 3 soon and opening it up under the same licensing as TensorFlow (Apache 2.0). It was reasonably complete before Swift 3 and I plan to have the Swift 3 version complete before the end of 2016, sans mistakes from original, and including lessons learned.

body: I have been working on a painful private project for a while using Swift. I'll be migrating the project API library to Swift 3 soon and [opening it up](https://gitlab.com/Omnijar/Ocular) under the same licensing as TensorFlow (Apache 2.0). It was reasonably complete before Swift 3 and I plan to have the Swift 3 version complete before the end of 2016, sans mistakes from original, and including lessons learned.
